{"tid":1354994,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今天不小心把心愛的山墳打碎了","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T00:32:54.000Z","uid":154406,"like":130,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"68c9df8f427bff2a801db26def228c2603a8e3c1","tid":1354994,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"今天不小心把心愛的山墳打碎了 事後我用了十五分鐘去細心欣賞 發現打碎了瓦磚碎 竟然比起平日那個形態更美 然後我再用了十分鐘去打掃地方 再為其拍照 這短短的三十分鐘 算是今天我思緒最安穩的時間 打碎了的山墳 是我今天看過最美好的東西 而那瓦礫著地的那一聲 是聽過最美好的聲音 原來人生覺得最爛的事情 也未必是最糟 因為最糟的 可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現 又或者根本就是自己 我想我找到了答案"},{"pid":"397fcde0fff2c8da37912eb23ccbb6519b1907b5","tid":1354994,"uid":154406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5386eab4427d486f829e590ab6e2c6b8509e188","tid":1354994,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad61b042b07ddb55bdd5bcff79d43ddb2967999","tid":1354994,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574d4bd5353d6a61e6c18983c1d766e572e33cec","tid":1354994,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dc728718cc2612a250053f4c1307c5f4bbb599","tid":1354994,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.g